text: AHA Gafur Chowdhury is a Jatiya Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Cox's Bazar-4 in 1986. == Career == Chowdhury was elected to parliament from Cox's Bazar-4 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986 Bangladeshi general election. == References == Category:Living people Category:People from Cox's Bazar District Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
